  Officer Moyihan was released from the hospital Friday after weeks of recovery . 
  Video shows him opening the driver-side door to talk to West after the car was pulled over during a shootout . 
  West immediately shoots Officer Moynihans under the face at close range . 
  He then fires at the other officers as he runs across the street . 
